      "description": "Offered for sale is a mint-condition example that has been exceptionally well kept and presents the way serious buyers hope to find one. It is clean inside and out, shows extremely well, and does not have the visible wear, neglect, or needs you typically see on older vehicles. This is not a project or an average driver-grade car\u2014it is a standout, well-preserved example that should appeal to someone looking for a top-condition vehicle they can enjoy and be proud to own.",
