      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking dependable basic transportation at an affordable entry point. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but offers solid utility, straightforward ownership, and excellent potential as a budget commuter, backup vehicle, or project. A sensible way to get on the road without overspending.",
